overview.en: The Bridge is aimed at proposing a safer extensible oracle machine network more sensitive to the price and more complying with market requirements in which everyone can participate to meet the current and future potential market needs.
overview.zh: Bridge 旨在提出一种更安全、对价格更灵敏、更符合市场要求人 人可参与的可扩展预言机网络，用以满足现有及未来可能的市场需求。
